Production Actors

  • This card will use a widget to link place data from D-LoD. None of that data will be editable in the card.
  • Production Actor ID will be removed in production migration.
  • Production Actor Role can be added and editied in the card.
  • The Production Actor Note can be added and edited in the card.

Production Places

  • This card will use a widget to link place data from D-LoD. None of that data will be editable in the card.
  • Production Place ID will be removed in production migration.
  • The Production Place Note can be added and edited in the card.

Production Techniques

  • All fields can be added and edited in the card.

Production Time Span

  • All fields can be added and edited in the card.
